{"tid":1598403,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[天文jj] 香港人有權幫天體改名 - 將個名同今年連結埋一齊!","createTime":"2019-09-27T12:17:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T09:13:09.000Z","uid":96609,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"da038c98768efe8b0030da89b9a854204b34bc5b","tid":1598403,"uid":96609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:17:09.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲，細佬連登CD-ROM嚟，借個朋友acc出post。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知好多巴絲而家唔會有心機理其他嘢，但我覺得下面呢樣嘢同樣可以紀念香港今年光輝嘅一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (其實我9月頭就發現咗，但拖到而家先搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">香港地區系外行星世界命名活動</div></strong><br />\n原因: 國際天文聯會(IAU) &rArr; 紀念成立一百週年 <br />\n&rArr; 在世界各地舉行系外行星命名活動<br />\n&rArr; 不同地區的民眾都可以為一顆系外行星及其母體恆星命名<br />\n<br />\n過程: 提名活動接受全港市民與 &rarr; 方案經評審及公眾投票將交予IAU審批 &rArr; 通過後將成為國際認可的名字<br />\n<br />\n<strong>香港地區:</strong><br />\n1. 分配予香港作命名的系外行星的編號: <strong>HD 212771</strong><br />\n2. 位於寶瓶座<br />\n3. 中文增補星名為「羽林軍增一」<br />\n4. 主星的視星等為7.6等，距離太陽系約364光年。該恆星光譜類型為G8IV，表面溫度為5121K (4848 C)，比太陽低11%，直徑是太陽的5倍，光度是太陽的18倍，質量是太陽的1.15倍。<br />\n<br />\nHD 212771位置圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.space.museum/image/image_gallery-98d40f17-8f62-4054-bf22-b81e2bcba63e.html?uuid=98d40f17-8f62-4054-bf22-b81e2bcba63e&amp;groupId=2178963&amp;t=1568776932981\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.space.museum%2Fimage%2Fimage_gallery-98d40f17-8f62-4054-bf22-b81e2bcba63e.html%3Fuuid%3D98d40f17-8f62-4054-bf22-b81e2bcba63e%26groupId%3D2178963%26t%3D1568776932981&h=5919c35c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(NASA HD 212771: <a href=\"https://exoplanets.nasa.gov/exoplanet-catalog/6905/hd-212771-b/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexoplanets.nasa.gov%2Fexoplanet-catalog%2F6905%2Fhd-212771-b%2F&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=c1518ee8\" target=\"_blank\">https://exoplanets.nasa.gov/exoplanet-catalog/6905/hd-212771-b/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n1. HD 212771所擁有的行星則編作HD 212771b<br />\n2. 中文星名亦可編為「羽林軍增一b」，質量是木星的2.3倍，表面溫度457K(184&deg;C)，公轉週期為373地球日，與HD212771相距1.22個天文單位（約1.8億公里）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.space.museum/image/image_gallery-f4b651db-42fa-45f4-aecd-b1cfa193b374.html?uuid=f4b651db-42fa-45f4-aecd-b1cfa193b374&amp;groupId=2178963&amp;t=1568776932981\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.space.museum%2Fimage%2Fimage_gallery-f4b651db-42fa-45f4-aecd-b1cfa193b374.html%3Fuuid%3Df4b651db-42fa-45f4-aecd-b1cfa193b374%26groupId%3D2178963%26t%3D1568776932981&h=726d6710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(NASA HD 212771b 個page: <a href=\"https://exoplanets.nasa.gov/exoplanet-catalog/6905/hd-212771-b/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fexoplanets.nasa.gov%2Fexoplanet-catalog%2F6905%2Fhd-212771-b%2F&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=c1518ee8\" target=\"_blank\">https://exoplanets.nasa.gov/exoplanet-catalog/6905/hd-212771-b/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n3. IAU 規定的命名規則：<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>3.1. 命名可以是具有長期文化歷史意義或地理意義，並值得透過命名天體來紀念的人、地方或事物</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3.13. 不允許提出以下類型的命名提案<br />\nii. 與政治、軍事、宗教人物有關的地點或事件名稱</span><br />\n<br />\n話就話個名唔可以有政治成份，但我知道連登仔女一定有辦法。<br />\n港共同中共啲大粒佬未必會理呢啲活動(小學維尼邊會識<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，就算知道都未必會哂心機去嘈(雖然而家西方學術界都好多中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 。到時如果入到圍甚至成功左，隨時大陸狗以後研究起嚟望住個名篤眼篤鼻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即使同2019有關嘅名都入唔到，都希望有其他名入到，我唔知而家有幾多份application，但如果俾啲最鍾意充人數嘅19愛國社團尻填改埋啲大陸柒名，到時仲難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁同香港有關嘅星體就成世孭住呢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得番三日咋，希望咁多位巴絲出手一齊為香港度個好名出嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nLink 喺下面:<br />\n太空館<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.space.museum/zh_TW/web/spm/activity/iau100/name-exoworlds.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.space.museum%2Fzh_TW%2Fweb%2Fspm%2Factivity%2Fiau100%2Fname-exoworlds.html&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=5ca69674\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.space.museum/zh_TW/web/spm/activity/iau100/name-exoworlds.html</a><br />\n國際天文聯會香港天文推廣組<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.iaunochk.org/2019/08/523/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iaunochk.org%2F2019%2F08%2F523%2F&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=b89a723c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.iaunochk.org/2019/08/523/</a><br />\n香港地區系外行星世界命名活動 - 規則及參加辦法<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.iaunochk.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/IAU100-NameExoWorlds-Guide_ec_v5.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iaunochk.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2FIAU100-NameExoWorlds-Guide_ec_v5.pdf&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=128263ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.iaunochk.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/IAU100-NameExoWorlds-Guide_ec_v5.pdf</a><br />\nIAU NameExoWorlds:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nameexoworlds.iau.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nameexoworlds.iau.org%2F&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=a5cea380\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nameexoworlds.iau.org/</a><br />\nIAU - Assigned Planetary System to HK<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nameexoworlds.iau.org/hong-kong-china\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nameexoworlds.iau.org%2Fhong-kong-china&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=783e6a4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nameexoworlds.iau.org/hong-kong-china</a>"},{"pid":"568e21f63566bf2cfcde32bee5a1b6cbb5d94de1","tid":1598403,"uid":40804,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T12:18:01.000Z","m