citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:33:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"862d7095636cb247257b3dd65886b717cdefb176","tid":1598403,"uid":96609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T09:13:09.000Z","msg":"借朋友acc自推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有idea 嘅巴絲快手啲填form<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.iaunochk.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/NameExoWorlds-Nomination-Form_v7.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.iaunochk.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2FNameExoWorlds-Nomination-Form_v7.pdf&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=cd385880\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.iaunochk.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/NameExoWorlds-Nomination-Form_v7.pdf</a><br />\nsend 去呢個email: nameexoworlds@iaunochk.org<br />\n今日last day 啦!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}